A vast network of glowing blue pneumatic tubes stretching across a retro-futuristic cityscape at dusk, with small capsules containing miniature paper documents zooming through the transparent tubes in multiple directions. The tubes connect towering Art Deco buildings with copper and brass fixtures, steam venting from junction points where tubes split and merge. In the foreground, one capsule arrives at a receiving station with a soft golden glow, while another launches from a sending station across the way. The sky is painted in warm oranges and deep purples, with vintage airships floating in the distance. The entire scene has a warm sepia-tinted color palette with pops of electric blue from the active tubes, evoking 1920s retrofuturism meets steampunk aesthetic. The composition emphasizes the synchronized flow and precise timing of the document delivery system, with motion blur on the fastest-moving capsules.
